                     <interp inst="t18591024-898-offence-1" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18591024-898-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp>, Stealing 1 pewter-pot, value 2<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., the property of <persName id="t18591024-name-36" type="victimName">
